# Solo Map Comparison Engine Rule

When editing this repository:

- Put shared scoring and eligibility logic in `src/comparison_engine/engine.py`.
- Put domain-specific product data in `data/*.json`.
- Preserve API compatibility under `/v1` unless intentionally releasing a breaking version.
- Update MCP tools when adding public API capabilities.
- Add tests for each new plugin or decision rule.
- Keep financial comparisons explicit about assumptions and warnings.
